# ovh_vrack_vpss (Data Source)

Use this data source to retrieve the list of VPS services attached to a vRack.

## Example Usage

{{tffile "examples/data-sources/vrack_vpss/example_1.tf"}}

## Argument Reference

* `service_name` - (Required) The service_name of your vRack.

## Attributes Reference

(See generated docs/data-sources/vrack_vpss.md for the full attribute list.)

* `id` - The ID of the data source.
* `result` - The list of VPS service names attached to this vRack.
